      "comment": "WICKED CONFESSION (2) is a progressive Victorian mare who won three on the trot including the rich Running of the Bulls at Birchip before drawing on the second line and working when runner-up last start at Bendigo. Should enjoy better favours from this draw. NAMAKA (10) was a big improver when she came from a similar draw to this to miss narrowly at this circuit and distance last week. Fitter again third up so could go one better. ISLA ROCHELLE (8) draws wider but did a good job to place in both a heat and the final of the Riverina Championships. Stablemate SIREN SEA (6) comes through the same series and wasn't far away from the placings in either round. Include.",
